    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>A dense opaque glass of a red or black color made at the glassworks of Count von Buquoy in southern Bohemia in the 19th century.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
